brs_objectives:
&lt;p&gt;To consult with stakeholders at all levels on how single use plastic can be replaced in the entire chain from import to consumption and establish a baseline using the inventory toolkit developed in the BRS-NORAD 1 project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;To also run a pilot project at stores, create three zero-plastic high schools and propose recommendations accompanied by an implementation plan to decisionmakers. 
Involve locals in the production of replacement bags 
Indirectly: reduce environmental pollution caused by plastics.&lt;/p&gt;

